commit.message: Make author property in CommitDetails optional to avoid errors if it is missing in JSON.
Create RecentCommitViewModel so that custom cell does not need to know intricacies of Commit object.
Create custom tableview cell - use it's properties/IBOutlets instead of using viewWithTag() to access labels.
Move model classes to actual model class file.
Change name of commit property in Commit model to commitDetails. Added CodingKeys enum to make Decodable still work.
Embed in NavigationController, use large titles.
Add GitHubAPIService class, call it from AppDelegate to test at startup.

Merge pull request #1 from crampsalot/work

Add sample JSON. Updated README with API url used.
